    "body": "Since `leave` prevents a function from being inlined, we could also think about employing heavier machinery to remove it, even if it is not the last statement:\r\n```\r\nfunction f(x) {\r\n  a()\r\n  if x {\r\n    b()\r\n    leave\r\n  }\r\n  c()\r\n}\r\n->\r\nfunction f(x) {\r\n  a()\r\n  switch x\r\n  case 0 {\r\n    c()\r\n  }\r\n  default {\r\n    b()\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n```",
